<section class="bg-[#F0EBD8] py-[80px] px-[20px] font-['DM_Sans',sans-serif]">
  <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto">

    <h2 class="text-[28px] md:text-[36px] font-bold mb-[50px] text-black tracking-[1px] font-['Playfair_Display',serif]">
      FAQS
    </h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-[30px]">

      <div class="bg-white p-[30px] md:p-[40px] rounded-[4px] shadow-[0_2px_8px_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)] hover:cursor-pointer hover:scale-108 transition-all">
        <h3 class="text-[14px] font-bold mb-[16px] text-black tracking-[0.5px] leading-[1.4]">
          WHAT IS INDOOR DIGITAL SIGNAGE ADVERTISING?
        </h3>
        <p class="text-[#333] leading-[1.7] text-[15px]">
          It's the placement of your ads on TV screens located inside high-traffic venues,
          offering brand visibility where people are already engaged.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-[30px] md:p-[40px] rounded-[4px] shadow-[0_2px_8px_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)] hover:cursor-pointer hover:scale-108 transition-all">
        <h3 class="text-[14px] font-bold mb-[16px] text-black tracking-[0.5px] leading-[1.4]">
          DO YOU OFFER PACKAGES THAT INCLUDE SCREENS AND ONLINE ADS?
        </h3>
        <p class="text-[#333] leading-[1.7] text-[15px]">
          Yes! We offer bundled packages that combine <strong>indoor billboards</strong> with digital
          marketing services like <strong>social ads</strong>, Google Ads, and SEO to maximize your reach
          both online and offline.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-[30px] md:p-[40px] rounded-[4px] shadow-[0_2px_8px_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)] md:col-[1/2] hover:cursor-pointer hover:scale-108 transition-all">
        <h3 class="text-[14px] font-bold mb-[16px] text-black tracking-[0.5px] leading-[1.4]">
          CAN YOU HELP MY BUSINESS RANK ON GOOGLE?
        </h3>
        <p class="text-[#333] leading-[1.7] text-[15px]">
          Absolutely. We provide SEO services, Google Business setup, and local search
          strategies to help your business show up when customers are searching for your
          services in Denver.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>